    "description": "Toggle Tile is a puzzle game that has you changing the color of tiles in a 3 by 3 grid.<br>The goal is to change the color of all the tiles. Each tile has a 3 by 3 grid of icons inside it.<br>Each icon acts on the corresponding tile in the puzzle. Click on a tile to apply all its effects at once.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165730/extras/8775dc8e2c12654bcf9283d22d95dfde.poster.avif?t=1729165593\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165730/extras/8775dc8e2c12654bcf9283d22d95dfde.webm?t=1729165593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165730/extras/8775dc8e2c12654bcf9283d22d95dfde.mp4?t=1729165593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Tiles can act on themselves, creating a dynamic board state.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165730/extras/bb8d2403eccd259d0d25373cd9022d78.poster.avif?t=1729165593\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165730/extras/bb8d2403eccd259d0d25373cd9022d78.webm?t=1729165593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165730/extras/bb8d2403eccd259d0d25373cd9022d78.mp4?t=1729165593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features a restart button...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165730/extras/e4365dc6e48819fe0b7183bdd17e67b2.poster.avif?t=1729165593\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite